; Regression test for issue #1085: Floating point exception with -X to a zero-priced currency (BZ#1085)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/1085
; The original bug caused a SIGFPE crash when using -X to exchange into/from a zero-priced currency.
; The fix ensures ledger exits cleanly (exit code 0) without crashing.

P 2024/01/01 EUR $0.00

2024/01/01 Test
    Assets:Checking   100 EUR
    Income:Salary

test bal -X '$'
end test
